      • AdvancedFiniteStateMachine

        public AdvancedFiniteStateMachine(java.lang.Class<? extends STATE> enumeration,
                                  T opMode)
                           throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Creates an Finite State Machine with the states described in the class declaration of the enum. The OpMode is a reference to your OpMode to get the dependencies of state, and inject them into the state
        Parameters:
        enumeration - the class of the enum containing the states
        opMode - the active OpMode to get dependencies from
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException

      • AdvancedFiniteStateMachine

        public AdvancedFiniteStateMachine(STATE[] states,
                                  T opMode)
                           throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Creates a Finite State Machine with the given AdvancedFiniteStateMachine.State array being the available states. The OpMode is a reference to your OpMode to get the dependencies of state, and inject them into the state
        Parameters:
        states - an array of states
        opMode - the active OpMode to get dependencies from
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - when either the states or opMode parameter is null

      • AdvancedFiniteStateMachine

        public AdvancedFiniteStateMachine(STATE state,
                                  T opMode)
                           throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Creates a Finite State Machine with the given start AdvancedFiniteStateMachine.State. The rest of the states are then infered to be the other elements within the enum that the start state is. The OpMode is a reference to your OpMode to get the dependencies of state, and inject them into the state
        Parameters:
        state - the start state of the Finite State Machine
        opMode - the active OpMode to get dependencies from
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - when either the states or opMode parameter is null
